  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 14th level your continuous exposure to poisons has left you more resilient than most.</p><p> You gain resistance to poison damage and have advantage on saving throws that would inflict the envenomed condition.</p><p> Once per turn, when you or your puppet hit a creature with a weapon or taijutsu attack you can spend one use of your Poison Kit to force them to make a saving throw against a poison in your possession.</p><p> Alternatively, as an action, your puppet can expend both uses of a poison to produce a cloud of poison in a 15-foot radius forcing all creatures to make a Constitution saving throw or suffer the effects of the poison.</p><p></p>",
